Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.92,0:02:01.01,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(850,0)\pos(1245,822)}Episode 3: "My Youth With Dio"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.01,0:02:01.01,Main,Jonathan,0,0,0,,I was able to find the antidote...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.07,0:02:03.81,Main,Jonathan,0,0,0,,I've already given it to my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.94,0:02:08.27,Main,Jonathan,0,0,0,,Dio... this pains me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.27,0:02:12.82,Main,Jonathan,0,0,0,,I never expected to have to deliver the man who was raised to be my brother over to the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.82,0:02:15.07,Main,Jonathan,0,0,0,,It's a shame... Dio...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.07,0:02:19.12,Main,Jonathan,0,0,0,,You probably don't believe me, but that is how I honestly feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.37,0:02:24.08,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,This is the kindness I've come to expect from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.68,0:02:30.78,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Jojo... I realize it's selfish, but I have one last request...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.22,0:02:34.25,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Please, let me have some time...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.25,0:02:36.24,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Just enough so I can surrender myself to the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.83,0:02:38.07,Thoughts,Jonathan,0,0,0,,Unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.07,0:02:42.64,Thoughts,Jonathan,0,0,0,,I was certain that he would struggle, attacking like a cornered beast!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.65,0:02:45.53,Thoughts,Dio,0,0,0,,Jojo... {Needs moar o's...idk why mudasubs did this in the beginning -Fadeout4}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.53,0:02:48.07,Thoughts,Dio,0,0,0,,How in the bloody hell did you escape from the slums alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.07,0:02:49.71,Thoughts,Dio,0,0,0,,I have no other choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.71,0:02:52.73,Thoughts,Dio,0,0,0,,I'll have to wait until he lowers his guard, then gut him with my knife!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.73,0:02:55.79,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Please, I regret the wicked life I've led up until now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.79,0:02:59.78,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,I was born into poverty, and it led me to pursue such foolish ambitions!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.41,0:03:02.27,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,I've been such an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.27,0:03:06.04,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,The fact that I would harm my benefactor over his fortune...  after all the kindness he's shown me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.59,0:03:09.88,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,I returned here because I wanted to turn myself in!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.88,0:03:13.74,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Why else would I return when I could have fled anywhere in the world?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.74,0:03:15.25,Main,Jonathan,0,0,0,,Th-that's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.79,0:03:18.05,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,I want to pay for my crimes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.05,0:03:18.84,Main,Jonathan,0,0,0,,Dio...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.84,0:03:21.11,Main,Speedwagon,0,0,0,,I'd be careful, Mr. Joestar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.11,0:03:23.34,Main,Speedwagon,0,0,0,,You can't trust a word this scoundrel says!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.30,0:03:26.80,Main,Speedwagon,0,0,0,,You must be wondering who I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.80,0:03:29.06,Main,Speedwagon,0,0,0,,Allow me to introduce myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.50,0:03:32.36,Main,Speedwagon,0,0,0,,Speedwagon's the name, and meddling's my game! {Liberties, lit. "I'm the Interfering Speedwagon}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.36,0:03:36.69,Main,Speedwagon,0,0,0,,I met the good Mr. Joestar here in the slums of London, so I accompanied him to help keep an eye out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.28,0:03:41.70,Main,Speedwagon,0,0,0,,Mr. Joestar, I've grown fond of you and your naiveté, so let me tell you something...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.70,0:03:46.78,Main,Speedwagon,0,0,0,,I've lived in the underworld my entire life, \Nand I've met scoundrels of every sort.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.78,0:03:50.71,Main,Speedwagon,0,0,0,,I can tell a good man from a rotten one just by their scent...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.58,0:03:53.37,Main,Speedwagon,0,0,0,,This bastard stinks!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.37,0:03:56.60,Main,Speedwagon,0,0,0,,He reeks worse than the lowest gutter trash I've ever met!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.60,0:04:00.55,Main,Speedwagon,0,0,0,,I've never met a scoundrel of his caliber in my entire life!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.55,0:04:03.22,Main,Speedwagon,0,0,0,,So you say your upbringing turned you into a bastard?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.22,0:04:04.18,Main,Speedwagon,0,0,0,,A likely story! {liberties, lit "that's wrong!"}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.51,0:04:07.20,Main,Speedwagon,0,0,0,,You've been evil since the day you were born!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.39,0:04:13.35,Main,Speedwagon,0,0,0,,Perhaps, you recall... this face?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.90,0:04:18.90,Main,Speedwagon,0,0,0,,This easterner confessed to selling you the poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.35,0:04:22.15,Main,George,0,0,0,,I heard everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.57,0:04:25.11,Main,George,0,0,0,,I am truly sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.65,0:04:31.62,Main,George,0,0,0,,I tried to raise you with the same \Nhope and affection as I have for my own son...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.30,0:04:35.96,Main,Jonathan,0,0,0,,Father, you shouldn't be out of bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.96,0:04:39.09,Main,George,0,0,0,,Very well... I shall return to my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.67,0:04:42.84,Main,George,0,0,0,,I have no desire to see my son taken away in chains.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.84,0:04:45.44,Main,George,0,0,0,,Jojo, please see to the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.44,0:04:46.11,Main,Jonathan,0,0,0,,Yes, father.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.22,0:04:49.47,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,I suppose this is the end, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.47,0:04:52.44,Main,Wang Chang,0,0,0,,That boy will not be detained.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.12,0:04:56.72,Main,Wang Chang,0,0,0,,I can see it written on his face, evident by the three birthmarks on his ear...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.72,0:04:59.86,Main,Wang Chang,0,0,0,,He was born under the star of great fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.61,0:05:06.86,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Jojo... the least you could do is be the one to put the cuffs on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.86,0:05:08.68,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,For everything we've been through these seven years...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.44,0:05:10.34,Main,Jonathan,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.98,0:05:13.87,Main,Speedwagon,0,0,0,,Watch yourself, Mr. Joestar!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.30,0:05:18.98,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Jojo... I suppose there are limits to the abilities of humankind...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.06,0:05:22.45,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,If there is one thing I have learned in my short life...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.32,0:05:29.68,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,The more you plot and scheme, the less likely it becomes things will go according to plan...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.27,0:05:32.58,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,One would have to be more than human to overcome that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.58,0:05:35.14,Main,Jonathan,0,0,0,,What are you saying? What do you mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.14,0:05:38.74,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,I'm through with being a mere mortal, Jojo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.62,0:05:42.82,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,I will transcend humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.82,0:05:44.82,Main,Jonathan,0,0,0,,The stone mask?! Why do you have it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.82,0:05:45.82,Main,Speedwagon,0,0,0,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.82,0:05:47.07,Main,Constable,0,0,0,,Shoot him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.07,0:05:49.57,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,And I'll use your blood to do it, Jojo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.00,0:05:56.95,Main,Speedwagon,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.59,0:06:00.87,Main,Jonathan,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.39,0:06:11.39,Main,Constable,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.16,0:06:28.46,Main,George,0,0,0,,Jojo...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.03,0:06:30.85,Main,Jonathan,0,0,0,,F-Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.41,0:06:36.16,Main,Jonathan,0,0,0,,I could have dodged that knife...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.86,0:06:39.50,Main,Jonathan,0,0,0,,But I was so distracted by the stone mask...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.29,0:06:41.94,Main,Jonathan,0,0,0,,And in my stead, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.50,0:06:46.51,Main,George,0,0,0,,Take this...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.18,0:06:50.47,Main,George,0,0,0,,This ring belonged to your late mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.65,0:06:53.01,Main,Jonathan,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.01,0:06:56.17,Main,Speedwagon,0,0,0,,That knife wound is most certainly fatal...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.17,0:06:58.56,Main,Speedwagon,0,0,0,,Damn it, I was supposed to keep this from happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.14,0:07:02.77,Main,Constable,0,0,0,,Lord Joestar! This is what I was talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.25,0:07:09.34,Main,Constable,0,0,0,,This is my fault! If only I had thrown Dio Brando's father behind bars!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.34,0:07:11.24,Main,Speedwagon,0,0,0,,His father...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.05,0:07:20.17,Main,Constable,0,0,0,,It wasn't long after I joined the police force that we caught a man who was trying to sell a stolen ring...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.17,0:07:24.37,Main,Constable,0,0,0,,That man was Dio's father... Dario Brando!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.77,0:07:28.59,Main,George,0,0,0,,Indeed, this matches my ring...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.18,0:07:32.21,Main,George,0,0,0,,My wife and I had a matching pair made especially for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.79,0:07:37.10,Main,Constable,0,0,0,,We caught a thief by the name of Brando trying to sell it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.21,0:07:39.32,Main,George,0,0,0,,Brando?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.10,0:07:44.74,Main,Constable,0,0,0,,Lord Joestar thought Brando had saved his life...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.45,0:07:47.38,Main,Constable,0,0,0,,But it was all a ruse!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.38,0:07:53.06,Main,Constable,0,0,0,,He was just a sneaky rat who tried to loot the wreckage of an accident!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.82,0:07:55.74,Main,Dario,0,0,0,,Bloody hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.01,0:08:02.69,Main,George,0,0,0,,Tell me... Did he say that I had willingly given him that ring?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.69,0:08:04.50,Main,Constable,0,0,0,,Yes sir, that he did!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.50,0:08:06.35,Main,Constable,0,0,0,,What a load of rubbish!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.35,0:08:08.38,Main,George,0,0,0,,That was no lie...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.38,0:08:10.79,Main,George,0,0,0,,I sent him that ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.79,0:08:13.26,Main,Constable,0,0,0,,W-What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.65,0:08:15.07,Main,George,0,0,0,,He's innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.59,0:08:17.54,Main,George,0,0,0,,There is no reason to detain him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.54,0:08:19.77,Main,Constable,0,0,0,,Why?! Why would you let him get away with this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.24,0:08:25.27,Main,George,0,0,0,,I might have done the same thing, had I been born into poverty...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.37,0:08:31.24,Main,George,0,0,0,,Please take this... Sell it, and buy something for your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.65,0:08:36.62,Main,George,0,0,0,,And please... Turn your life around, do not stray from the path of good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.20,0:08:43.50,Main,Constable,0,0,0,,Lord Joestar knew the truth, and he still agreed to take Dio in!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.50,0:08:47.50,Main,Jonathan,0,0,0,,Father, please stay strong... The doctors can save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.01,0:08:52.13,Main,George,0,0,0,,Jojo, please don't hold this against Dio...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.13,0:08:54.38,Main,George,0,0,0,,This was all my fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.05,0:08:58.99,Main,George,0,0,0,,I was far too strict, even with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.99,0:09:03.89,Main,George,0,0,0,,I can only imagine how that must have made Dio feel... {check?}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.40,0:09:07.89,Main,George,0,0,0,,It must have pushed him to do this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.67,0:09:13.90,Main,George,0,0,0,,Please... bury Dio alongside his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.75,0:09:15.72,Main,Jonathan,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.40,0:09:23.41,Main,George,0,0,0,,It's not so bad, Jojo... Being able to die...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.41,0:09:27.96,Main,George,0,0,0,,In the arms of... my son...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.87,0:09:35.65,Main,People,0,0,0,,Lord Joestar!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.93,0:09:44.73,Main,Constable,0,0,0,,It was his kindness that led to all of this! It was all for nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.73,0:09:45.73,Main,Speedwagon,0,0,0,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.46,0:09:52.17,Main,Speedwagon,0,0,0,,That man's kind-hearted spirit has been\N passed down to his son, Jonathan Joestar!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.17,0:09:57.74,Main,Speedwagon,0,0,0,,It will become the flame that drives him, his source of strength, lighting the path to his future!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.74,0:10:02.96,Main,Speedwagon,0,0,0,,Normally, I can't stand naïve fools who cry whenever life sends hardship their way...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.95,0:10:05.75,Main,Speedwagon,0,0,0,,But this family is an exception...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.25,0:10:11.21,Main,Speedwagon,0,0,0,,They have absolute faith in their course of action! They're true men, through and through!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.06,0:10:16.91,Main,Speedwagon,0,0,0,,The... the body!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.91,0:10:20.00,Main,Speedwagon,0,0,0,,Where is Dio Brando's body?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.05,0:10:25.19,Main,Speedwagon,0,0,0,,Constable, get away from that window!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.39,0:10:41.73,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Wrrryyyyyy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.99,0:10:46.70,Main,Speedwagon,0,0,0,,The constable's head!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.16,0:10:51.17,Main,Speedwagon,0,0,0,,W-What's the meaning of this?! How is he still alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.17,0:10:54.50,Main,Policeman,0,0,0,,How could he survive those gunshots?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.50,0:10:57.01,Main,Policeman,0,0,0,,Be careful! He must have a weapon on him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.38,0:11:02.05,Main,Jonathan,0,0,0,,I-Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.55,0:11:05.60,Main,Policeman,0,0,0,,H-He's heading this way...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.60,0:11:08.27,Main,Speedwagon,0,0,0,,What are you doing? Shoot him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.35,0:11:10.39,Main,Jonathan,0,0,0,,Dio, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.48,0:11:16.28,Main,Jonathan,0,0,0,,D-Dio!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.28,0:11:22.45,Main,Speedwagon,0,0,0,,Don't be reckless, Jojo! Just shoot him! You have to!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.39,0:11:54.94,Main,Speedwagon,0,0,0,,He... He's still alive... He was shot in the head, and he's still...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.94,0:11:56.44,Main,Speedwagon,0,0,0,,What is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.44,0:12:00.44,Main,Speedwagon,0,0,0,,What's going on?! Because I haven't the foggiest idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.44,0:12:02.45,Main,Jonathan,0,0,0,,How is this possible?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.16,0:12:03.82,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Jojo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.20,0:12:10.33,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Witness the incredible power I now possess... I owe it to the stone mask!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.33,0:12:12.21,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Not to mention your father's blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.84,0:12:18.96,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Wrrrryyy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.51,0:12:22.76,Main,Jonathan,0,0,0,,He's draining his blood... and drawing energy from it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.51,0:12:27.39,Main,Jonathan,0,0,0,,What happened that you turned into this, Dio?! {This might be better with some rewording or something. I wanted to split into 2 lines, but there's no time where that would make sense. -Fadeout4}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.57,0:12:42.70,Thoughts,Jonathan,0,0,0,,My head is spinning...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.70,0:12:45.28,Thoughts,Jonathan,0,0,0,,The knife... my father's death... his blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.28,0:12:47.91,Thoughts,Jonathan,0,0,0,,Dio... the stone mask... my research...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.91,0:12:51.00,Thoughts,Jonathan,0,0,0,,The brain... strange abilities... untold power!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.75,0:12:54.00,Thoughts,Jonathan,0,0,0,,Is Dio no longer human?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.00,0:12:56.50,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Wrryyyy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.76,0:13:02.72,Thoughts,Jonathan,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.10,0:13:11.60,Main,Speedwagon,0,0,0,,D-Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.60,0:13:13.48,Main,Speedwagon,0,0,0,,He's unstoppable!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.48,0:13:15.56,Main,Speedwagon,0,0,0,,I've never seen a monster like that before!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.56,0:13:19.65,Main,Speedwagon,0,0,0,,I've never seen a beast with that kind of otherworldly power!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.36,0:13:21.15,Main,Jonathan,0,0,0,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.28,0:13:24.53,Main,Jonathan,0,0,0,,To be quite honest, I'm terrified.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.53,0:13:25.28,Main,Jonathan,0,0,0,,But Dio...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.65,0:13:27.78,Main,Jonathan,0,0,0,,I cannot allow you to remain in this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.78,0:13:30.33,Main,Jonathan,0,0,0,,I've inherited this responsibility, and I will put an end to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.33,0:13:33.04,Main,Speedwagon,0,0,0,,Mr. Joestar, don't! He'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.16,0:13:34.96,Thoughts,Jonathan,0,0,0,,The brain!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.96,0:13:40.92,Thoughts,Jonathan,0,0,0,,Those spines in the stone mask must unlock some kind of hidden potential in the human brain!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.92,0:13:43.30,Thoughts,Jonathan,0,0,0,,Which means there might still be a chance to defeat him...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.31,0:13:53.77,Main,Speedwagon,0,0,0,,A corpse!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.77,0:13:58.06,Main,Zombeh,0,0,0,,Blood... I want to lap it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.15,0:14:09.41,Main,Zombeh,0,0,0,,Blood... just let me drink some of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.25,0:14:24.21,Main,Jonathan,0,0,0,,Monster or not... it still pains me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.21,0:14:27.97,Main,Jonathan,0,0,0,,Father... please give me the strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.14,0:14:32.01,Main,Jonathan,0,0,0,,I have to be strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.01,0:14:34.97,Main,Jonathan,0,0,0,,Because Dio isn't human anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.97,0:14:36.18,Main,Jonathan,0,0,0,,He's a demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.81,0:14:37.60,Main,Speedwagon,0,0,0,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.65,0:14:44.32,Main,Jonathan,0,0,0,,I won't let you slaughter another innocent person!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.20,0:14:49.86,Main,Speedwagon,0,0,0,,H-He stopped it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.61,0:14:53.87,Main,Speedwagon,0,0,0,,It went through his hand and he still stopped it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.62,0:14:58.79,Main,Speedwagon,0,0,0,,And the wound on his head is gone... it's already healed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.79,0:15:01.67,Main,Speedwagon,0,0,0,,Immortal... He really is immortal, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.17,0:15:08.17,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Weak! You're still a weakling!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.51,0:15:17.52,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Jojo... {Seriously? O_o}{No :p}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.52,0:15:19.35,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,A little more...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.35,0:15:23.73,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,I'd like to have a little more fun with this magnificent power...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.31,0:15:28.57,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,I still haven't tested the extent of my abilities, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.99,0:15:33.20,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Hiding, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.01,0:15:50.01,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Remember what I said, Jojo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.01,0:15:54.55,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Plot and scheme all you want, humans will always be slaves to their limitations.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.26,0:15:57.85,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,I would stop struggling if I were you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.85,0:16:02.02,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Come out from behind that curtain!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.23,0:16:08.73,Main,Jonathan,0,0,0,,This isn't some scheme... This is courage! {this line bothers me}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.16,0:16:20.37,Main,Speedwagon,0,0,0,,His wounds are healing, even though he's on fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.37,0:16:23.54,Main,Speedwagon,0,0,0,,That's the reason behind his immortality!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.54,0:16:25.54,Main,Jonathan,0,0,0,,This fire won't be enough to stop him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.55,0:16:35.22,Main,Speedwagon,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.64,0:16:40.02,Main,Jonathan,0,0,0,,Get to safety, Speedwagon! This isn't your fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.37,0:16:59.53,Main,Speedwagon,0,0,0,,There's no chance to escape if you go up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.53,0:17:02.08,Main,Speedwagon,0,0,0,,The fire is spreading to the entire mansion!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.17,0:17:09.88,Thoughts,Speedwagon,0,0,0,,Mr. Joestar... what are you thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.80,0:17:16.64,Main,Jonathan,0,0,0,,Come up here, Dio!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.19,0:17:29.77,Main,Jonathan,0,0,0,,Dio! I won't let you and that unearthly power escape into the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.77,0:17:31.78,Main,Speedwagon,0,0,0,,Mr. Joestar, don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.74,0:17:40.28,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,You're trying to keep me distracted...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.28,0:17:42.45,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,So that your friend can escape...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.33,0:17:44.62,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.83,0:17:52.59,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,I'll heal these burns by draining the life from you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.34,0:17:57.88,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Useless, useless, useless, useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.88,0:18:02.22,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,I can fall from this height and not even feel a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.02,0:18:07.52,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,And you've just backed yourself into a dead end!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.77,0:18:11.69,Main,Jonathan,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.99,0:18:19.28,Main,Jonathan,0,0,0,,Father, I'll miss you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.28,0:18:22.33,Main,Jonathan,0,0,0,,Rise up to heaven, along with these burning embers...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.33,0:18:23.33,Main,Jonathan,0,0,0,,And... {just "And..."?}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.33,0:18:31.08,Main,Jonathan,0,0,0,,Please lend these flames the strength to do what must be done!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.25,0:18:36.55,Main,Speedwagon,0,0,0,,Mr. Joestar... what are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.13,0:18:41.60,Main,Speedwagon,0,0,0,,No... you can't be planning to...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.60,0:18:45.39,Main,Speedwagon,0,0,0,,No... you mustn't do what I think you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.35,0:18:50.35,Thoughts,Jonathan,0,0,0,,He's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.40,0:18:55.07,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Wrryyyyyyy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.28,0:19:01.07,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Weak! Weak as always!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.70,0:19:05.58,Narrator,Jonathan,0,0,0,,At that moment, Jojo's entire youth flashed before his eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.17,0:19:18.76,Thoughts,Jonathan,0,0,0,,My youth... the youth I spent with Dio!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.26,0:19:23.51,Main,Jonathan,0,0,0,,That youth... ends here, once and for all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.22,0:19:26.85,Main,Speedwagon,0,0,0,,Mr. Joestar wants the fire to burn hotter!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.85,0:19:32.77,Main,Speedwagon,0,0,0,,Hot enough to burn that monster to cinders before he can heal!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.77,0:19:34.48,Main,Speedwagon,0,0,0,,Just to defeat Dio!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.23,0:19:40.49,Main,Speedwagon,0,0,0,,That's why he's gone to the roof, he's waiting for the fire to grow stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.45,0:19:43.12,Main,Speedwagon,0,0,0,,Don't!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.79,0:19:49.79,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,You worm! How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.46,0:19:54.63,Thoughts,Jonathan,0,0,0,,Joestar Manor... the home I grew up in is burning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.63,0:20:00.97,Thoughts,Jonathan,0,0,0,,My father is dead... I've lost everything... Everything but my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.09,0:20:06.26,Thoughts,Jonathan,0,0,0,,But I'm willing to see that burn, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.26,0:20:10.31,Thoughts,Jonathan,0,0,0,,Whatever it takes, Dio... As long as I can put an end to that twisted power you wield!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.14,0:20:13.85,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Goodbye, Jojo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.31,0:20:19.82,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,It was only for a moment, but your resolve managed to impress me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.32,0:20:23.66,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Now cry tears of joy, for you will be able to die alongside your father!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.66,0:20:24.70,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,You buffoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.32,0:20:31.75,Thoughts,Dio,0,0,0,,I have surpassed humanity! I am immortal, invincible! I can rule the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.75,0:20:34.58,Thoughts,Dio,0,0,0,,This is the power you have given me, Jojo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.55,0:20:48.10,Main,Jonathan,0,0,0,,Too high!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.85,0:20:54.19,Main,Jonathan,0,0,0,,Dio!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.19,0:20:56.02,Main,Jonathan,0,0,0,,I'm not finished with you! {Too divergent?}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.02,0:20:57.77,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,W-What?! You-
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.52,0:21:01.44,Main,Jonathan,0,0,0,,I'm not letting go this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.44,0:21:04.45,Main,Jonathan,0,0,0,,Dio, I'm going to make you face your fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.45,0:21:07.20,Main,Jonathan,0,0,0,,With the knife--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.20,0:21:12.37,Main,Jonathan,0,0,0,,With the knife that you used to kill my father!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.87,0:21:16.96,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Wrrryyyyyy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.55,0:21:25.05,Thoughts,Dio,0,0,0,,The bones in both of his arms should be shattered!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.05,0:21:28.51,Thoughts,Dio,0,0,0,,And his body is in flames, so why won't he loosen his grip?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.51,0:21:32.81,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Very well! Let us plunge into the inferno together!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.81,0:21:35.39,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,But you will be the only one to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.39,0:21:40.32,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,My body is nigh invulnerable, I have the power to escape the flames no matter how hot they burn!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.65,0:21:43.24,Main,Jonathan,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.24,0:21:45.95,Main,Jonathan,0,0,0,,Give me the last of your strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.95,0:21:48.74,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,He cries out... A cry that could no longer be heard!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.74,0:21:51.91,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,Perhaps his words were able to reach his father's soul...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.91,0:21:56.79,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,Or perhaps he instinctively used the home he grew up in to his advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.46,0:21:58.29,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,He kicked!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.29,0:22:00.54,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,And after kicking that wall...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.54,0:22:02.55,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.51,0:22:06.47,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,The guardian of the Joestar estate:
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.01,0:22:08.84,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,A statue of the Goddess of Love!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.85,0:22:15.64,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,How dare you?! You think you can do this to-
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.69,0:22:18.69,Thoughts,Dio,0,0,0,,I... I forgot...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.69,0:22:23.90,Thoughts,Dio,0,0,0,,My fatal error... was forgetting the way his anger can explode...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.74,0:22:27.86,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Jojo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.86,0:22:30.91,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,It can't end... not like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.91,0:22:33.91,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,My... life...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.75,0:22:41.96,Main,Speedwagon,0,0,0,,Mr. Joestar!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.26,0:22:46.46,Main,Jonathan,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.92,0:22:48.22,Main,Speedwagon,0,0,0,,You're alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.93,0:22:50.47,Main,Speedwagon,0,0,0,,He's alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.05,0:22:52.60,Main,Speedwagon,0,0,0,,He beat Dio...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.39,0:22:57.56,Main,Speedwagon,0,0,0,,He won!
